  <p class="mt-4 color-fg-muted text-center">By clicking &ldquo;Sign up for GitHub&rdquo;, you agree to our <a class="Link--inTextBlock" href="<%= GitHub.help_url %>/terms" target="_blank">terms of service</a> and
